Karen Lamm https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Karen_Lamm 0 Karen Lamm (June 21, 1952 – June 29, 2001) was an American character actress and producer. She was known for Thunderbolt and Lightfoot (1974), The Unseen (1980) and Trackdown (1976). She was married to musicians Dennis Wilson and Robert Lamm.
